{"type":"message","id":"e25a2d4b","parentId":"b77f8508","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:37:30.292Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-edf1f5003d7443eca524c51cfa4df0f5","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<a href=\"https://wappass.baidu.com/static/captcha/tuxing_v2.html?&amp;logid=11156780888395115072&amp;ak=c27bbc89afca0463650ac9bde68ebe06&amp;backurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baidu.com%2Fs%3Fwd%3DPCB%2B%E7%BC%BA%E9%99%B7%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%2BAI%2B%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%2B%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B&amp;ext=x9G9QDmMXq%2FNo87gjGO0Pywa9z%2FETWt3FtTBVWaedjwsr0rrDszYO2sAbAnT1vLIUgqUK9LXd1cIlztrhMwiv5LGqKWhTZD8Q7xZpGkscD7N27TG8uvv8SLCyIOEZ97r&amp;signature=a5d8ded4eda6ecd1cc2f97ea389c0af8&amp;timestamp=1772411850\">Found</a>."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":866,"aggregated":"<a href=\"https://wappass.baidu.com/static/captcha/tuxing_v2.html?&amp;logid=11156780888395115072&amp;ak=c27bbc89afca0463650ac9bde68ebe06&amp;backurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baidu.com%2Fs%3Fwd%3DPCB%2B%E7%BC%BA%E9%99%B7%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%2BAI%2B%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%2B%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B&amp;ext=x9G9QDmMXq%2FNo87gjGO0Pywa9z%2FETWt3FtTBVWaedjwsr0rrDszYO2sAbAnT1vLIUgqUK9LXd1cIlztrhMwiv5LGqKWhTZD8Q7xZpGkscD7N27TG8uvv8SLCyIOEZ97r&amp;signature=a5d8ded4eda6ecd1cc2f97ea389c0af8&amp;timestamp=1772411850\">Found</a>.","cwd":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772411850288}}
{"type":"message","id":"811ba4e6","parentId":"e25a2d4b","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:37:47.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，代理端口连接正常，但直接搜索遇到了一些技术问题。让我尝试用更系统的方式来调研PCB生产工厂中目标检测AI模型的应用情况。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-5aa4248370f14d3286d2f03b39533415","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"PCB_AI_调研计划.md","content":"# PCB生产工厂目标检测AI模型应用调研计划\n\n## 调研目标\n了解目标检测AI模型在PCB生产工厂中的实际应用场景、技术方案和效果\n\n## 主要应用场景\n1. PCB缺陷检测\n   - 焊点缺陷检测\n   - 线路断裂检测\n   - 短路检测\n   - 元器件缺失检测\n   - 极性错误检测\n\n2. 质量管控\n   - 自动光学检测(AOI)\n   - X射线检测\n   - 外观质量检查\n\n3. 生产流程优化\n   - 生产进度监控\n   - 设备状态监测\n   - 物料识别分类\n\n## 技术调研方向\n1. 常用AI模型\n   - YOLO系列\n   - Faster R-CNN\n   - SSD\n   - Mask R-CNN\n\n2. 数据集要求\n   - PCB缺陷图像数据集\n   - 标注标准\n   - 数据增强技术\n\n3. 部署方案\n   - 边缘计算部署\n   - 云端推理\n   - 实时检测要求\n\n## 需要收集的信息\n- 行业案例研究\n- 技术白皮书\n- 厂商解决方案\n- 实际应用效果数据\n- 成本效益分析"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ds-v3","model":"ds-v3","usage":{"input":14247,"output":330,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14577,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772411850293}}
