{"type":"message","id":"75db8bed","parentId":"312a1cb1","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:41:44.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"          老板，代理连接测试显示网络是通的，但搜索时遇到了一些限制。让我分析一下可能的原因："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-3780504ca3e74b4fba64e07d4e1e2191","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"网络访问分析.md","content":"# 网络访问问题分析\n\n## 当前状态\n- 代理服务器：10.30.44.154:1111 ✅ 连接正常\n- 基础网络：可以访问Google首页 ✅\n- 搜索功能：受限 ❌\n\n## 可能的原因\n\n### 1. 代理服务器限制\n- 可能只允许特定类型的流量\n- 可能限制了搜索类请求\n- 可能有频率限制\n\n### 2. 目标网站防护\n- Google Scholar有严格的机器人检测\n- IEEE Xplore需要机构订阅\n- 学术网站对代理IP敏感\n\n### 3. 认证要求\n- 部分学术资源需要登录\n- 可能需要机构VPN或账号\n\n## 解决方案建议\n\n### 短期方案\n1. 使用企业内网资源库\n2. 联系IT部门开通特定访问权限\n3. 使用已有的技术文档和报告\n\n### 长期方案\n1. 申请学术数据库访问权限\n2. 建立内部知识库\n3. 与高校或研究机构合作\n\n## 替代调研方法\n1. 行业报告购买（如Gartner、IDC）\n2. 厂商技术白皮书直接获取\n3. 参加行业技术交流会\n4. 咨询专业系统集成商"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ds-v3","model":"ds-v3","usage":{"input":20986,"output":325,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21311,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772412086195}}
{"type":"message","id":"c01d72d0","parentId":"75db8bed","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:41:44.582Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-3780504ca3e74b4fba64e07d4e1e2191","toolName":"write","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully wrote 460 bytes to 网络访问分析.md"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772412104578}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb80a5f4","parentId":"c01d72d0","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:41:55.473Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"      老板，网络连接本身是通的，但遇到了学术网站的访问限制。这很常见，因为：\n\n1. **学术网站防护严格** - Google Scholar、IEEE等对代理IP和机器人访问很敏感\n2. **可能需要认证** - 很多学术资源需要机构订阅或登录\n3. **代理服务器策略** - 可能只允许基础网页浏览，限制搜索功能\n\n建议我们可以：\n- 联系IT部门开通专门的学术资源访问权限\n- 直接联系厂商获取技术白皮书\n- 使用企业内部已有的技术文档库\n\n您希望我尝试其他调研方式，还是先基于现有知识为您深入分析某个技术方向？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ds-v3","model":"ds-v3","usage":{"input":21326,"output":137,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21463,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772412104582}}
{"type":"message","id":"d900c138","parentId":"eb80a5f4","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:45:56.013Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-02 00:45 UTC] 那你就深度检索可以直接搜到的资源"}],"timestamp":1772412356004}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a1518f7","parentId":"d900c138","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:46:05.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"          好的老板，我立即深度检索可以直接访问的资源。让我尝试不同的搜索策略来获取PCB目标检测的相关信息。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-a738adcb8ccc4a72af0d63530edc7db2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"export HTTP_PROXY=\"http://10.30.44.154:1111\" && export HTTPS_PROXY=\"http://10.30.44.154:1111\" && curl -s \"https://github.com/search?q=PCB+defect+detection\" | grep -i \"repository\" | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ds-v3","model":"ds-v3","usage":{"input":21492,"output":106,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772412356012}}
