{"type":"compaction","id":"7f2bfd2d","parentId":"11fcddb9","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:47:05.685Z","summary":"## Goal\nResearch practical applications of object detection AI models in PCB manufacturing factories, specifically focusing on defect detection, quality control, and technical implementation.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Must communicate in Chinese\n- Use specified proxy for web access: HTTP_PROXY=\"http://10.30.44.154:1111\", HTTPS_PROXY=\"http://10.30.44.154:1111\"\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Created PCB_AI_调研计划.md with research framework\n- [x] Created PCB_AI_技术文档综述.md with technical architecture overview\n- [x] Created 网络访问分析.md with network access issue analysis\n- [x] Tested proxy connectivity (successful for basic access)\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Collecting academic papers and industry technical documents on PCB defect detection\n\n### Blocked\n- Web search tools require Brave API key (missing_brave_api_key error)\n- Academic websites (Google Scholar, IEEE Xplore, arXiv) blocking access with 403/400 errors despite working proxy\n- Baidu requiring captcha verification\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Switched to technical documentation creation**: Due to web access limitations, shifted focus to creating comprehensive technical frameworks based on existing knowledge\n- **Proxy configuration tested and confirmed**: Basic connectivity works but search functionality remains restricted\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Contact IT department to resolve academic resource access permissions\n2. Reach out to manufacturers (Cognex, Keyence) directly for technical whitepapers\n3. Explore internal enterprise knowledge base resources\n4. Consider purchasing industry reports from Gartner/IDC if web access cannot be resolved\n\n## Critical Context\n- Proxy server: 10.30.44.154:1111 (confirmed working for basic access)\n- Created files: PCB_AI_调研计划.md, PCB_AI_技术文档综述.md, 网络访问分析.md\n- Error details: missing_brave_api_key, ENOENT for memory files, 403/400 errors from academic sites\n- User is referred to as \"老板\" (boss) in Chinese context\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\n- Retrieve information about PCB defect detection from directly accessible resources\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Use direct resource access (no external API/tool restrictions mentioned)\n- Focus on GitHub repositories related to PCB defect detection\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Set up proxy configuration for network access\n- [x] Executed initial GitHub search query for \"PCB defect detection\" repositories\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Analyzing search results from GitHub\n- [ ] Filtering and evaluating relevant repositories\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Used proxy configuration**: To ensure network access through specified proxy server\n- **Focused on GitHub search**: As primary source for PCB defect detection resources\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Parse and analyze the GitHub search results\n2. Extract relevant repository links and descriptions\n3. Provide summarized findings to user\n\n## Critical Context\n- Proxy settings: HTTP_PROXY=\"http://10.30.44.154:1111\", HTTPS_PROXY=\"http://10.30.44.154:1111\"\n- Search query: \"PCB defect detection\" on GitHub\n- Current output being processed: grep-filtered repository listings from curl response\n\n[Large toolResult (~29K tokens) omitted from summary]","firstKeptEntryId":"11fcddb9","tokensBefore":50244,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
{"type":"message","id":"0200a41d","parentId":"7f2bfd2d","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:47:11.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到您正在研究PCB缺陷检测的AI应用，并且已经通过代理成功访问了GitHub搜索。让我帮您分析这些搜索结果并提取有价值的信息。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-a2305bcc7d914fed979bd8151d5ab40b","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"PCB_AI_调研计划.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ds-v3","model":"ds-v3","usage":{"input":12890,"output":52,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12942,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772412425798}}
{"type":"message","id":"10e3e150","parentId":"0200a41d","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:47:11.162Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-a2305bcc7d914fed979bd8151d5ab40b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# PCB生产工厂目标检测AI模型应用调研计划\n\n## 调研目标\n了解目标检测AI模型在PCB生产工厂中的实际应用场景、技术方案和效果\n\n## 主要应用场景\n1. PCB缺陷检测\n   - 焊点缺陷检测\n   - 线路断裂检测\n   - 短路检测\n   - 元器件缺失检测\n   - 极性错误检测\n\n2. 质量管控\n   - 自动光学检测(AOI)\n   - X射线检测\n   - 外观质量检查\n\n3. 生产流程优化\n   - 生产进度监控\n   - 设备状态监测\n   - 物料识别分类\n\n## 技术调研方向\n1. 常用AI模型\n   - YOLO系列\n   - Faster R-CNN\n   - SSD\n   - Mask R-CNN\n\n2. 数据集要求\n   - PCB缺陷图像数据集\n   - 标注标准\n   - 数据增强技术\n\n3. 部署方案\n   - 边缘计算部署\n   - 云端推理\n   - 实时检测要求\n\n## 需要收集的信息\n- 行业案例研究\n- 技术白皮书\n- 厂商解决方案\n- 实际应用效果数据\n- 成本效益分析"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772412431158}}
{"type":"message","id":"218ce4f3","parentId":"10e3e150","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:47:15.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-f2c0294eb49a401a970f1be7b526e005","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"PCB_AI_技术文档综述.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ds-v3","model":"ds-v3","usage":{"input":13210,"output":21,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13231,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772412431163}}
{"type":"message","id":"896dc113","parentId":"218ce4f3","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:47:15.165Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-f2c0294eb49a401a970f1be7b526e005","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# PCB目标检测AI模型技术文档综述\n\n## 一、核心技术架构\n\n### 1.1 主流AI模型应用\n- **YOLO系列**：实时检测，适合产线高速检测\n  - YOLOv5/v7/v8：平衡速度与精度\n  - 适用于焊点、元器件检测\n- **Faster R-CNN**：高精度检测\n  - 适合精细缺陷识别\n  - 计算资源要求较高\n- **SSD**：单阶段检测器\n  - 速度较快，精度适中\n- **Mask R-CNN**：实例分割\n  - 用于精确的缺陷区域定位\n\n### 1.2 数据集构建要求\n- **图像采集标准**：\n  - 分辨率：至少1024x768像素\n  - 光照条件：均匀照明，无阴影\n  - 角度：正射角度，避免透视变形\n- **标注规范**：\n  - 缺陷类型分类标准\n  - 边界框标注精度要求\n  - 数据增强策略\n\n## 二、典型应用场景\n\n### 2.1 缺陷检测类型\n1. **焊点缺陷**\n   - 虚焊、冷焊\n   - 焊锡过多/过少\n   - 焊桥短路\n\n2. **线路缺陷**\n   - 线路断裂\n   - 线路短路\n   - 线路宽度异常\n\n3. **元器件缺陷**\n   - 缺失元器件\n   - 错件\n   - 极性错误\n   - 偏移/倾斜\n\n### 2.2 检测精度要求\n- **检测率**：>99.5%\n- **误检率**：<0.1%\n- **处理速度**：<100ms/图像\n\n## 三、技术挑战与解决方案\n\n### 3.1 主要挑战\n- 小目标检测精度\n- 光照变化影响\n- 相似缺陷区分\n- 实时性要求\n\n### 3.2 解决方案\n- 多尺度特征融合\n- 数据增强技术\n- 集成学习策略\n- 边缘计算优化\n\n## 四、部署实施方案\n\n### 4.1 硬件配置\n- **GPU要求**：NVIDIA Jetson系列或RTX显卡\n- **相机系统**：工业级高分辨率相机\n- **照明系统**：均匀LED环形光源\n\n### 4.2 软件架构\n- 模型训练平台\n- 推理服务部署\n- 数据管理系统\n- 质量监控界面\n\n## 五、效益分析\n\n### 5.1 质量提升\n- 缺陷检出率提升30-50%\n- 人工复检工作量减少80%\n\n### 5.2 成本节约\n- 人工成本降低\n- 返工率下降\n- 客户投诉减少\n\n## 六、行业趋势\n- 端到端自动化检测\n- 多模态融合检测\n- 自适应学习系统\n- 云端协同检测"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772412435160}}
{"type":"message","id":"67a2c509","parentId":"896dc113","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:47:24.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"          基于您的调研计划和现有技术文档，让我帮您分析GitHub上的PCB缺陷检测相关资源。从之前的搜索结果中，我看到有很多有价值的开源项目。让我为您整理关键发现："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-9444b4599ac94cef9d9d597fb8208aec","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -x http://10.30.44.154:1111 -s \"https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=PCB+defect+detection&sort=stars&order=desc\" | head -50","env":{"HTTP_PROXY":"http://10.30.44.154:1111","HTTPS_PROXY":"http://10.30.44.154:1111"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ds-v3","model":"ds-v3","usage":{"input":13871,"output":143,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14014,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772412435165}}
