{"type":"message","id":"954aedd8","parentId":"ce33ef76","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:58:51.145Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-d2cb53b85e7d4507b8225ea08f4dc5e3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"name\": \"Smart-Power-Safety-Detection-Dataset-Deep-Learning-YOLOV8-Model-Training-Grid-Insulation-Gloves-Wear\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/QQ767172261\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/QQ767172261/Smart-Power-Safety-Detection-Dataset-Deep-Learning-YOLOV8-Model-Training-Grid-Insulation-Gloves-Wear\",\n      \"description\": \"智慧电力安全检测数据集 深度学习YOLOV8模型训练 电网绝缘手套穿戴检测数据集 深度学习在电力安全智慧电力方面的应用 (1)\",\n      \"name\": \"AI-Safety-Space-Station-YoloV12\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/pranay-kondapalli\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/pranay-kondapalli/AI-Safety-Space-Station-YoloV12\",\n      \"description\": \"YOLOv12 Safety Object Detection Project uses deep learning to detect safety gear like helmets, gloves, and suits in real-time. Trained on Falcon datasets and deployed via Docker, it enables fast, accurate safety compliance monitoring in environments such as space stations, industries, and construction sites.\",\n      \"name\": \"Object-Detection-using-YOLOv5-on-Gloved-Hands-vs-Bare-Hands-Images-Dataset\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/ManikaNagpal\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/ManikaNagpal/Object-Detection-using-YOLOv5-on-Gloved-Hands-vs-Bare-Hands-Images-Dataset\",\n      \"description\": \"This repository demonstrates an object detection pipeline using YOLOv5 to identify gloved hands and bare hands in images.\",\n      \"name\": \"MLB_GloveTracking_TransferLearning\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/TheDanGriff\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/TheDanGriff/MLB_GloveTracking_TransferLearning\",\n      \"description\": \"Transfer learning for glove tracking: code to fine-tune the pretrained YOLO model on the baseball_rubber_home_glove dataset and evaluate performance.\","}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4076,"aggregated":"\"name\": \"Smart-Power-Safety-Detection-Dataset-Deep-Learning-YOLOV8-Model-Training-Grid-Insulation-Gloves-Wear\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/QQ767172261\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/QQ767172261/Smart-Power-Safety-Detection-Dataset-Deep-Learning-YOLOV8-Model-Training-Grid-Insulation-Gloves-Wear\",\n      \"description\": \"智慧电力安全检测数据集 深度学习YOLOV8模型训练 电网绝缘手套穿戴检测数据集 深度学习在电力安全智慧电力方面的应用 (1)\",\n      \"name\": \"AI-Safety-Space-Station-YoloV12\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/pranay-kondapalli\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/pranay-kondapalli/AI-Safety-Space-Station-YoloV12\",\n      \"description\": \"YOLOv12 Safety Object Detection Project uses deep learning to detect safety gear like helmets, gloves, and suits in real-time. Trained on Falcon datasets and deployed via Docker, it enables fast, accurate safety compliance monitoring in environments such as space stations, industries, and construction sites.\",\n      \"name\": \"Object-Detection-using-YOLOv5-on-Gloved-Hands-vs-Bare-Hands-Images-Dataset\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/ManikaNagpal\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/ManikaNagpal/Object-Detection-using-YOLOv5-on-Gloved-Hands-vs-Bare-Hands-Images-Dataset\",\n      \"description\": \"This repository demonstrates an object detection pipeline using YOLOv5 to identify gloved hands and bare hands in images.\",\n      \"name\": \"MLB_GloveTracking_TransferLearning\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/TheDanGriff\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/TheDanGriff/MLB_GloveTracking_TransferLearning\",\n      \"description\": \"Transfer learning for glove tracking: code to fine-tune the pretrained YOLO model on the baseball_rubber_home_glove dataset and evaluate performance.\",","cwd":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772413131138}}
{"type":"message","id":"e456b775","parentId":"954aedd8","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:59:03.367Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                    太好了！找到了相关数据集。让我获取详细信息："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-c0f6c717900540a49a3ca4dba5cb5ab8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -x http://10.30.44.154:1111 -s \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ManikaNagpal/Object-Detection-using-YOLOv5-on-Gloved-Hands-vs-Bare-Hands-Images-Dataset/main/README.md\" | head -30","env":{"HTTP_PROXY":"http://10.30.44.154:1111","HTTPS_PROXY":"http://10.30.44.154:1111"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ds-v3","model":"ds-v3","usage":{"input":27092,"output":129,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27221,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772413131145}}
{"type":"message","id":"f980cf26","parentId":"e456b775","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:59:05.232Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-c0f6c717900540a49a3ca4dba5cb5ab8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Object Detection of Gloved Hands vs Bare Hands using YOLOv5\n\nThis repository demonstrates **object detection using YOLOv5** to classify and locate **gloved hands** and **bare hands** in images. The project uses a **custom dataset** of hand images and includes scripts for training, validation, inference, visualization, and saving results in multiple formats.\n\n---\n\n## Features\n\n- Train YOLOv5 on a custom **gloved vs bare hand dataset**.\n- Perform **validation** and visualize results:\n  - Training & validation loss curves\n  - Confusion matrix\n  - Precision, Recall, and PR/F1 curves\n- Run **inference on test images** and visualize predictions.\n- Save **detection results** as images, text files, and **JSON files** for further analysis.\n- Export training, validation, and detection outputs for easy reuse.\n\n---\n\n## Dataset\nDownload the file in YOLOv5 format from [Roboflow](<https://universe.roboflow.com/glove-uylxg/glove-q7czq/dataset/1>) and upload it in your drive.\nThe dataset contains labeled images of hands, categorized as:\n\n- `gloved_hand`\n- `bare_hand`\n\nIt is organized into **train**, **validation**, and **test** sets. \n\n---\n## Repository Structure"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1853,"aggregated":"# Object Detection of Gloved Hands vs Bare Hands using YOLOv5\n\nThis repository demonstrates **object detection using YOLOv5** to classify and locate **gloved hands** and **bare hands** in images. The project uses a **custom dataset** of hand images and includes scripts for training, validation, inference, visualization, and saving results in multiple formats.\n\n---\n\n## Features\n\n- Train YOLOv5 on a custom **gloved vs bare hand dataset**.\n- Perform **validation** and visualize results:\n  - Training & validation loss curves\n  - Confusion matrix\n  - Precision, Recall, and PR/F1 curves\n- Run **inference on test images** and visualize predictions.\n- Save **detection results** as images, text files, and **JSON files** for further analysis.\n- Export training, validation, and detection outputs for easy reuse.\n\n---\n\n## Dataset\nDownload the file in YOLOv5 format from [Roboflow](<https://universe.roboflow.com/glove-uylxg/glove-q7czq/dataset/1>) and upload it in your drive.\nThe dataset contains labeled images of hands, categorized as:\n\n- `gloved_hand`\n- `bare_hand`\n\nIt is organized into **train**, **validation**, and **test** sets. \n\n---\n## Repository Structure","cwd":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772413145225}}
