{"type":"message","id":"88f0a2d9","parentId":"af671af1","timestamp":"2026-03-02T01:00:08.148Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-d6abbb81c3a6444fb85e6a7afe96284b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"name\": \"Sarcasm-and-Toxicity-detection-in-Reddt-Comments-Using-GloVe\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/KokoMukruYves\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/KokoMukruYves/Sarcasm-and-Toxicity-detection-in-Reddt-Comments-Using-GloVe\",\n      \"description\": \"The project aimed at predicting  sarcasm and  toxicity based on Kaggle Sarcasm Headlines dataset using GloVe embeddings, Logistic Regression and Decision Tree Classifier.\",\n      \"name\": \"Toxic_Comment_Classification\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/AnubrataPal\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/AnubrataPal/Toxic_Comment_Classification\",\n      \"description\": \"Collected data from Kaggle. Pre-processed the dataset. Applied GloVe word embedding on LSTM model to achieve about 95% accuracy. Finally, showcased the results.\",\n      \"name\": \"sentiment-analysis-twitter-glove\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/lucalullo\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/lucalullo/sentiment-analysis-twitter-glove\",\n      \"description\": \"Notebook di analisi del sentiment su tweet (positivo/negativo) basato su una rete neurale LSTM bidirezionale. L’obiettivo è confrontare due strategie di word embedding: embedding appresi da zero sul dataset e embedding pre-addestrati GloVe, analizzando l’impatto sulle prestazioni del modello e sulla capacità di generalizzazione.\","}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3511,"aggregated":"\"name\": \"Sarcasm-and-Toxicity-detection-in-Reddt-Comments-Using-GloVe\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/KokoMukruYves\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/KokoMukruYves/Sarcasm-and-Toxicity-detection-in-Reddt-Comments-Using-GloVe\",\n      \"description\": \"The project aimed at predicting  sarcasm and  toxicity based on Kaggle Sarcasm Headlines dataset using GloVe embeddings, Logistic Regression and Decision Tree Classifier.\",\n      \"name\": \"Toxic_Comment_Classification\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/AnubrataPal\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/AnubrataPal/Toxic_Comment_Classification\",\n      \"description\": \"Collected data from Kaggle. Pre-processed the dataset. Applied GloVe word embedding on LSTM model to achieve about 95% accuracy. Finally, showcased the results.\",\n      \"name\": \"sentiment-analysis-twitter-glove\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/lucalullo\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/lucalullo/sentiment-analysis-twitter-glove\",\n      \"description\": \"Notebook di analisi del sentiment su tweet (positivo/negativo) basato su una rete neurale LSTM bidirezionale. L’obiettivo è confrontare due strategie di word embedding: embedding appresi da zero sul dataset e embedding pre-addestrati GloVe, analizzando l’impatto sulle prestazioni del modello e sulla capacità di generalizzazione.\",","cwd":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772413208143}}
