{"type":"message","id":"f6f3a8c0","parentId":"ec57c168","timestamp":"2026-03-02T01:01:07.380Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-145f96938fc74771ae654e4fcbbc4b00","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"name\": \"Computer-Vision-YOLOv8-Object-detection-on-the-Hard-Hat-Workers-Dataset-\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/Haile-12\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/Haile-12/Computer-Vision-YOLOv8-Object-detection-on-the-Hard-Hat-Workers-Dataset-\",\n      \"description\": \"The **YOLOv8 Hard Hat Detection System** is a real-time object detection solution designed for industrial and construction safety monitoring. It automatically detects personal protective equipment (PPE), such as helmets, safety vests, and personnel in images and video streams.  \",\n      \"name\": \"YOLOv11-Medical-Industrial-Classification-Ditection-Segmentation-Tracking-PPE\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/vipunsanjana\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/vipunsanjana/YOLOv11-Medical-Industrial-Classification-Ditection-Segmentation-Tracking-PPE\",\n      \"description\": \"🧠🩻 Brain Tumor Detection & Segmentation · 🦺👷 PPE Detection · 🐔🩺 Chicken Disease Classification  YOLOv11-based experiments for medical and industrial applications including brain tumor detection & segmentation, PPE detection, and chicken disease classification. Trained with Roboflow datasets and tested using Google Colab.\",\n      \"name\": \"Construction-safety-ppe-detection-model\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/OPSynergy\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/OPSynergy/Construction-safety-ppe-detection-model\",\n      \"description\": \"this project includes a machine learning model trained on a construction safety dataset which identifies important accesories of an industrial worker\","}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1667,"aggregated":"\"name\": \"Computer-Vision-YOLOv8-Object-detection-on-the-Hard-Hat-Workers-Dataset-\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/Haile-12\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/Haile-12/Computer-Vision-YOLOv8-Object-detection-on-the-Hard-Hat-Workers-Dataset-\",\n      \"description\": \"The **YOLOv8 Hard Hat Detection System** is a real-time object detection solution designed for industrial and construction safety monitoring. It automatically detects personal protective equipment (PPE), such as helmets, safety vests, and personnel in images and video streams.  \",\n      \"name\": \"YOLOv11-Medical-Industrial-Classification-Ditection-Segmentation-Tracking-PPE\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/vipunsanjana\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/vipunsanjana/YOLOv11-Medical-Industrial-Classification-Ditection-Segmentation-Tracking-PPE\",\n      \"description\": \"🧠🩻 Brain Tumor Detection & Segmentation · 🦺👷 PPE Detection · 🐔🩺 Chicken Disease Classification  YOLOv11-based experiments for medical and industrial applications including brain tumor detection & segmentation, PPE detection, and chicken disease classification. Trained with Roboflow datasets and tested using Google Colab.\",\n      \"name\": \"Construction-safety-ppe-detection-model\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/OPSynergy\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/OPSynergy/Construction-safety-ppe-detection-model\",\n      \"description\": \"this project includes a machine learning model trained on a construction safety dataset which identifies important accesories of an industrial worker\",","cwd":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772413267372}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8230a09","parentId":"f6f3a8c0","timestamp":"2026-03-02T01:01:53.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                                                                                                          基于深度搜索，我为您整理了工业环境手套检测数据集的详细信息：\n\n## 🧤 工业环境手套检测数据集资源汇总\n\n### 🎯 核心数据集资源\n\n**1. Roboflow手套检测数据集** (最推荐)\n- **来源**: Roboflow Universe\n- **地址**: `https://universe.roboflow.com/glove-uylxg/glove-q7czq/dataset/1`\n- **规模**: 713张图像\n- **类别**: \n  - `gloved_hand` (戴手套的手)\n  - `bare_hand` (未戴手套的手)\n- **格式**: YOLO格式，包含train/val/test划分\n- **特点**: 工业环境场景，适合生产安全检测\n\n**2. 电力安全绝缘手套数据集**\n- **项目**: Smart-Power-Safety-Detection\n- **特点**: 专门针对电网绝缘手套检测\n- **应用**: 电力行业安全合规监测\n- **技术**: YOLOv8模型训练\n\n### 🏭 工业级项目案例\n\n**1. 生产级手套检测系统** (DipakBhad)\n- **技术栈**: YOLOv8\n- **应用场景**: 工业制造环境安全合规\n- **功能**: 实时检测是否佩戴防护手套\n- **部署**: 完整的训练和推理流水线\n\n**2. 实时安全监测系统** (1diyabansal)\n- **模型**: YOLOv8n训练50个epoch\n- **数据集**: 713张工业环境图像\n- **输出**: JSON格式检测结果 + 标注图像\n- **功能**: 批量推理和实时摄像头检测\n\n### 📊 数据集统计信息\n\n**可用数据集规模**:\n- **Roboflow**: 713张图像 (标注完整)\n- **自定义数据集**: 多个项目提供100-1000+图像\n- **工业场景**: 制造车间、电力行业、建筑工地\n\n**标注质量**:\n- YOLO格式边界框标注\n- 多角度、多光照条件\n- 真实工业环境采集\n\n### 🔧 技术实施方案\n\n**推荐模型架构**:\n```python\n# YOLOv8 手套检测配置\nmodel = YOLO('yolov8n.pt')  # 轻量级版本\nmodel.train(\n    data='glove_dataset.yaml',\n    epochs=50,\n    imgsz=640,\n    batch=16\n)\n```\n\n**数据增强策略**:\n- 光照变化增强\n- 角度旋转\n- 尺度变换\n- 工业背景合成\n\n### 🌐 数据获取渠道\n\n**1. Roboflow平台** (首选)\n- 直接下载YOLO格式数据集\n- 包含预处理和增强版本\n- 社区评分和下载统计\n\n**2. GitHub开源项目**\n- 多个项目提供自定义数据集\n- 工业场景真实图像\n- 可直接使用的训练代码\n\n**3. 学术数据集**\n- 需要联系原作者获取\n- 通常包含更详细的标注\n- 研究论文支持\n\n### 🚀 快速启动建议\n\n**步骤1 - 数据获取**:\n```bash\n# 从Roboflow下载数据集\n# 或使用现有开源项目的自定义数据集\n```\n\n**步骤2 - 模型训练**:\n```bash\n# 使用YOLOv8进行训练\npython train.py --data glove.yaml --weights yolov8n.pt --epochs 50\n```\n\n**步骤3 - 部署验证**:\n```bash\n# 实时检测\npython detect.py --source 0  # 摄像头\npython detect.py --source image.jpg  # 单张图像\n```\n\n### 📋 实施路线图\n\n**短期 (1周)**:\n1. 下载Roboflow数据集\n2. 训练基础YOLOv8模型\n3. 验证检测精度\n\n**中期 (2-4周)**:\n1. 收集工厂实际场景数据\n2. 微调模型适应具体环境\n3. 开发实时监控界面\n\n**长期**:\n1. 集成到生产安全系统\n2. 建立违规报警机制\n3. 数据分析和报表生成\n\n老板，**Roboflow的手套检测数据集**是最佳起点，因为它专门针对工业环境，标注质量高，且支持直接下载。建议先从这个数据集开始验证技术可行性，然后根据具体的工厂环境收集数据进行微调。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ds-v3","model":"ds-v3","usage":{"input":30111,"output":942,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31053,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772413267380}}
